{
  "stem": "18581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in-- we tried to feed ourselves, which was not easy, because in the food lines, Poles would very often point out to the Jews in the line so that the Jews would be arrested and they would advance in the line.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was not so easy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then we heard from friends, the telephone or going through the backyards, one house to another, that there is a possibility to get out of town and to work in Baltoji Voke, or in Polish Biala-Waka, peat mine.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went there and we worked for a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember the date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would say probably the end of-- certainly the end of July, not later, maybe even earlier.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got ourselves organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were there at the peat mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had some contacts with some friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we decided that being in the area which is under the Lithuanian-- in Lithuanian district is not so good, because so many Lithuanians were infested with anit-Semitism at that time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we wanted to go further south, where we heard from farmers that the Jews in places like Dzieveniskes, Kalelishok, Varenavas, and others were still everybody in his home and the Germans didn't touch them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were no Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were mainly some local self-defense going, but not much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we decided to go south.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a few weeks at the peat mine, or maybe more than a few weeks, maybe-- maybe a month or so, we found-- a group of us, about 15, hired a truck.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we took us south.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that itself was not an easy thing, because Jews were not supposed to hire trucks, and certainly not move from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
